# /{{skill_name}}

Productized replacement for the clone-the-last-ticket {{workflow_name}} workflow. Parameterized,
phased, QC-gated, and **hard-halts before any external post**. Reads `.claude/config/stack.yaml` and
resolves all I/O through adapters (no hardcoded tools).

